NAME Houndsteeth Tower, Roof 
DAY_LIGHT 
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
The tower's roof is flat on top with a crenellated wall around the edges. From
here, watcher's can see to a distance of many miles in all directions. To the
